// @check
// @error-at 6:16 extra `>` in type annotation
// A `>>` where one `>` closes the generic banks a phantom `>` credit; it is
// reported and dropped at the annotation, not silently spent on the LATER
// unrelated `Box<i32>` annotation below (which parses clean).
type Box<T> = { v: T }
